Package: phytaxr
Title: Phytoplankton Taxonomic Curation Tools
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Fernando", "Rayón Viña", , "tu@email.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides tools for cleaning, standardizing, and resolving
    phytoplankton taxon names against external taxonomic databases (WoRMS,
    GBIF). Designed for use with the PhytoMAP database.
